.* Load a signed field or literal into a register                       00180000
.* This is a sub-macro for use by the $IF-macro only                    00190000
.*                                                                      00200000
&LABEL   IF$LS &REG,                   * Register to load              *00210000
               &FLD,                   * Field or literal with value   *00220000
               &LITLEN,                * Length of literal or 0 for fld*00230000
               &TYPE                   * Type of field                  00240000
